Package: kronos
Title: Automated Time Card Generation for Oracle OTL
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jonathan", "Payne", , "jon.payne@environment-agency.gov.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2551-5363"))
Description: Links Outlook calendar exports and daily time-keeping data to
    produce Oracle Time and Labour (OTL) forms. Supports aggregation and
    analysis of historical OTL data, flexi balance tracking, time allocation
    reporting, and objective comparison against quarterly targets. The daily
    hours spreadsheet is optional: when omitted, standard-day defaults are
    used with overrides from all-day calendar events.
